DISCLAIMER REGARDING LEGAL TEXTS:
This repository contains Brazilian legal texts (laws, decrees, resolutions, 
normative acts) that are in the public domain and not subject to copyright. 
No rights are claimed over the original legal texts themselves.

However, all work involving standardization, formatting, extraction, 
normalization, segmentation, metadata design, structural HTML generation, JSON 
schema creation, TXT compilation, indexing logic, file organization, and any 
other intellectual effort used to produce the structured versions of these 
documents is protected by copyright held by the author.

The rights granted under this license refer exclusively to the structured, 
processed, formatted, and organized output produced by the author, not to the 
public-domain legal texts.


